16[(III)] Public Interest Directors:-
(1)The names of public interest directors shall be forwarded to the Board after the approval of the Board of the stock exchange/clearing corporation. The shareholders approval shall not be necessary. A minimum of two names shall be submitted to the Board for each vacancy of public interest directors.
